daft enough to do it.

818
00:48:25,280 --> 00:48:27,576
Was he all right wi' you? Yeah.

819
00:48:27,600 --> 00:48:29,040
Can I eat this pizza cold?

820
00:48:30,280 --> 00:48:31,656
Yeah, why not?

821
00:48:31,680 --> 00:48:33,376
