831
00:48:59,480 --> 00:49:01,816
So, we might drive into Leeds
and look at some shops, so...

832
00:49:01,840 --> 00:49:05,280
..you can play with your Land Rover.
Love you! See ya. Bye.

833
00:49:26,280 --> 00:49:27,720
